name: Red Rigure On Red Water With Red Sky And Red Three
description:
Looking inside a gifted rose...
A red landscape through a red foggy night... 
Sitting and meditating... 
   Sitting at the edge of a table.... 
Looking at a piece of wood.... 
   A dark, gloomy, empty space....
A small, dark red, thin, beautiful mirror.... 
   The only thing missing is a face....
 The wild and profane...
The inner/outer voice....
A ritualized image...
 The figures seem to pivot...
  in a mental space... 
out of our visual field...
 sometimes walking forward... 
sometimes crouching.... 
   sometimes standing...
Its a gift for you...
  Good night....
    Travel.....
      Nicely.....
